describe the game

The game is a 2D multiplayer shooting game. We will be using a client-server and some Python to build the game. it have 3 life, each shot will take one life off from the plater

the client server will based on our personal server


Aplha project: a 2D multiplayer plateformer shooter game. Using client-server. 2 players will combat each other using guns, the player can jump, go forwards and backwards and crouch. Each player has 3 lives, when a player is touch by a bullet, he looses 1 life. The server will be accessible from anywhere in the world as well as within LANs.
